<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Thisan In! 52</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Aw pak un Pathien Belam No,
 Kalvari a thi kha;
 Nangmah leh keimah tatna di'n,
 A thisan a pawt tai.

[V2]
 Thisan in......thisanin,
 Ei tan tai, Belam No thisan in;
 Ei tan tai......ei tan tai,
 Belam No, Hallelujah pak un.

[V3]
 2. Aw Lalpa hehpih lopi chu,
 A hauhsak len guol loh;
 Sang tamtak A pie tai kei le,
 Vangsakna chu ei piei.

[V4]
 3. Hallelujah Lopina chu,
 Amah kumkhuon chang hen;
 Khawvel gilo leh kei Krista'
 Thisan lun in ei tan.</lyrics>
<author>Patea</author>
<hymn_number>56</hymn_number>
</song>